msgstr "`weight`"

#: ../../source/live2d.rst:173 ../../source/live2d.rst:190
msgid ""
"A float between 0.0 and 1.0, the weight by which the new value will change "
"the current value."
msgstr ""
"0.0 から 1.0 までの浮動小数点で、新しい値が現在の値を変更するウェイトになりま"
